##<a id="0-5-0"></a> v0.5.0

**Release Date:** October 4, 2019

<p class="note breaking"><strong>Breaking Change:</strong> This release is incompatible with the v0.4
  beta release of KSM.
  Before you install KSM v0.5, you must uninstall
  KSM v0.4 from <%= vars.ops_manager %>.
